text: Avdotyino () is a rural locality (a village) in Goretovskoye Rural Settlement of Mozhaysky District, Moscow Oblast, Russia. The population was 7 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == The village is located 19 km north-east from Mozhaysk, on the left bank of the Iskona River. == References == Category:Rural localities in Moscow Oblast
title: Avdotyino, Mozhaysky District, Moscow Oblast
